3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - Attention mechanisms are a key area of research in AI, and the paper proposes a new variant of the SE block that improves the performance of CNNs.
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper proposes a new attention mechanism that is based on convolutional layers, which are commonly used in neural networks. This falls under the domain of neural computing.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper evaluates the proposed C-Local block on the CIFAR-10 dataset, which is a popular dataset for image classification. This falls under the domain of multimedia research.
